  "detailed_description": "Katana Arena is a gory arena fighter with multiplayer support. Survive hordes of different enemies and defeat the final bosses in order to unlock new levels.<br><br><u><strong>Dynamic body slicing</strong></u><br>No pre-sliced bodies. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/e3bfed7ffd891dee33d16bcf3114c34d.poster.avif?t=1769972359\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/e3bfed7ffd891dee33d16bcf3114c34d.webm?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/e3bfed7ffd891dee33d16bcf3114c34d.mp4?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Damage camera</strong></u><br>Shows the bone breaking action with x-ray style and slow motion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/3672cb7d669444a116294161e08f7088.poster.avif?t=1769972359\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/3672cb7d669444a116294161e08f7088.webm?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/3672cb7d669444a116294161e08f7088.mp4?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Ragdoll system</strong></u><br>Send the enemies flying with your powerful kick or special skills. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/7148a2db08be2d637aeea4a569c64fcf.poster.avif?t=1769972359\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/7148a2db08be2d637aeea4a569c64fcf.webm?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/7148a2db08be2d637aeea4a569c64fcf.mp4?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Themed arenas</strong></u><br>Different themes like asian, medieval and roman.<br><br><u><strong>Character customization</strong></u><br>Change your outfit for your liking.<br><br><u><strong>Dynamic weather and daylight cycle</strong></u><br>Adjust the weather and daylight and/or let them be fully dynamic.<br><br><u><strong>Upgradeable skills</strong></u><br>Earn battle coins by killing enemies and upgrade your skills.<br><br><u><strong>Partial controller support</strong></u><br>Can be played with controller but most of the menus require mouse and keyboard.",
  "about_the_game": "Katana Arena is a gory arena fighter with multiplayer support. Survive hordes of different enemies and defeat the final bosses in order to unlock new levels.<br><br><u><strong>Dynamic body slicing</strong></u><br>No pre-sliced bodies. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/e3bfed7ffd891dee33d16bcf3114c34d.poster.avif?t=1769972359\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/e3bfed7ffd891dee33d16bcf3114c34d.webm?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/e3bfed7ffd891dee33d16bcf3114c34d.mp4?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Damage camera</strong></u><br>Shows the bone breaking action with x-ray style and slow motion.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/3672cb7d669444a116294161e08f7088.poster.avif?t=1769972359\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/3672cb7d669444a116294161e08f7088.webm?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/3672cb7d669444a116294161e08f7088.mp4?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Ragdoll system</strong></u><br>Send the enemies flying with your powerful kick or special skills. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/7148a2db08be2d637aeea4a569c64fcf.poster.avif?t=1769972359\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/7148a2db08be2d637aeea4a569c64fcf.webm?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006450/extras/7148a2db08be2d637aeea4a569c64fcf.mp4?t=1769972359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Themed arenas</strong></u><br>Different themes like asian, medieval and roman.<br><br><u><strong>Character customization</strong></u><br>Change your outfit for your liking.<br><br><u><strong>Dynamic weather and daylight cycle</strong></u><br>Adjust the weather and daylight and/or let them be fully dynamic.<br><br><u><strong>Upgradeable skills</strong></u><br>Earn battle coins by killing enemies and upgrade your skills.<br><br><u><strong>Partial controller support</strong></u><br>Can be played with controller but most of the menus require mouse and keyboard.",
